     Our solutions

     Invoicing & payment

   Invoicing & payment

Invoicing & payment

From invoice to payment, the multichannel world is your oyster!

   Regardless of your invoice format, their transmission mode or
   pertaining payment terms, DOCAPOSTE supports you in making all
   exchanges with your ecosystem electronic, in line with your specific
   professional and organisational requirements.


Our solutions

Make the most of our expertise in invoice and settlement automation.


   CUSTOMER & SUPPLIER INVOICES

   Whether you choose a paper or electronic format (OPTION 1, 2 or 3),
   DOCAPOSTE is by your side to implement a solution integrated to your
   Information System, in accordance with regulatory constraints.


   PAYMENT

   Centralised access to various settlement modes for your customers,
   invoice settlement follow-up, etc.
   Make management easier by integrating DOCAPOSTE's secure payment
   solution.


   ELECTRONIC ARCHIVING

   Access your information instantly in a secure and centralised manner,
   and gain in productivity thanks to our SaaS solution! Invoices, SEPA
   mandates, etc., this service enables you to archive, classify, view and
   share your documents.


Our strenghts

A financial performance solution

   Optimise the management of the Purchase to Pay process, reduce manual
   entries, simplify approval chains, reduce payment terms, facilitate
   supplier relations and enhance the efficiency of your financial
   exchanges.


Open and customisable tools

   DOCAPOSTE offers modular solutions that can easily be integrated into
   your company's Information System, whilst adapting to your business
   line's evolutions.


Experts at your disposal

   From consultancy to production launch, our experts are there to support
   you in your projects. Close to 9,000 customers - be they SMEs or key
   accounts - have benefited from our know-how and have entrusted us with
   the management of their invoices and payments.


Trust-based partnership

   Emphasize on trust with DOCAPOSTE! Document sealing, certified
   electronic signatures, probative archiving, evidence management,
   recovery or destruction of end-of-life archives...it is time for your
   exchanges to become traceable and transparent.


Security and reliability every step of the way

   As a subsidiary of the Group La Poste, DOCAPOSTE complies with NF
   Z42-013 and Z42-020 standards, is certified FNTC-TA and FNTC-CFE, and
   approved by the SIAF (French Interdepartmental Archiving Service). Your
   data are hosted in France within ISO 27001- and ISO 9001-certified DATA
   CENTRES.

